## Secrets (Bitwarden)
- `bw_get_secret "Item Name"` — auto-unlocks via `ensure_bw_session`
- Helpers: zsh (`~/.oh-my-zsh/custom/bitwarden.zsh`), fish (`~/.config/fish/functions/bw_*.fish`)
- Session file `~/.bw_session` stores raw token — shared across zsh and fish
- **Non-interactive shells** (Claude Code): run `export BW_SESSION=$(cat ~/.bw_session)` before `bw` commands
